## Cancelled Tender: W6431-230091/A

### General Information

* **Tender Reference Number**: PW-22-01008067
* **Tender Status**: Cancelled
* **Publication Date**: September 23, 2022
* **Tender Closing Date**: October 7, 2022 (14:00:00)

### Description

The tender notice for the "Cancelled-W6431-230091/A" has been cancelled. This notice was a Request for Proposals under the trade agreements for the following countries:

* Canada-Honduras Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-European Union Comprehensive Economic and Trade Agreement (CETA)
* World Trade Organization Agreement on Government Procurement (WTO GPA)
* Canada-Peru Free Trade Agreement (CPFTA)
* Canada-Panama Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-Korea Free Trade Agreement (CKFTA)
* Canada-UK Trade Continuity Agreement (Canada-UK TCA)
* Canada-Chile Free Trade Agreement (CCFTA)
* Canada-Colombia Free Trade Agreement
* Canada-Ukraine Free Trade Agreement (CUFTA)
* Comprehensive and Progressive Agreement for Trans-Pacific Partnership (CPTPP)
* Canadian Free Trade Agreement (CFTA)

The services required under this cancelled tender were related to Human Resource Services, Business Consulting/Change Management; Project Management Services.

### Location

* **Location of Opportunity**: Manitoba
* **Location of Delivery**: Manitoba

### Contact Information

* **Contact Name**: Leanne Cooper
* **Contact Email**: [leanne.cooper@forces.gc.ca](mailto:leanne.cooper@forces.gc.ca)
* **Contact Phone**: 613-392-2811 x 4541

### Note

Please note that the tender notice for this specific opportunity has been cancelled and is no longer available for bidding. Any interested parties may contact Leanne Cooper for further information.
